Create Sonoran desert lab time-series data

Source: R/get_retriever_data.R
get_sdl_data.Rd

Original data found here http://www.eebweb.arizona.edu/faculty/venable/LTREB/LTREB

get_sdl_data(plots = c(4, 7, 8, 9, 10, 11, 12, 14, 15, 16, 17),
  path = file.path(get_default_data_path(), "veg-plots-sdl"))

Arguments

plots

vector of plots to keep
path

where to load the raw data files from

Value

list of two dataframes (one with abundance data, the other with covariate data) and one list of metadata.

Examples

if (FALSE) {
  get_sdl_data(sdl_data_tables=retriever_data()$'veg-plots-sdl')
}
